#Example:

Educator submits → POST /response/

Admin edits question → PATCH /question/:id/

TextQuestionContainer

### POST /http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/container

purpose: Admin creates a text question container

# Optional Values
-description 

-is_active

# Mandatory values
-title

# Editable fields
-title

-description 

-is_active

### PATCH /http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/container

purpose: Admin edits a field of a text question container

# Editable fields

-title 

-description

# Non Editable fields

-is_active

-----------------------------------------

TextQuestion 
------------

### POST /http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/question

purpose: Admin creates text question

# Optional values

-is_active

# Mandatory values

-title 

-text_question_container

-question_number_id

# Editable fields

-title
-is_active

# Immutable fields

-question_number_id
-text_question_container


### PATCH /http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/question/2/

purpose:  An educator can edit a single text question 

# Optional values 

-title
-is_active

# Not editable

-question_number_id
-text_question_container

------------------------------------------


